view.name: Average Weekly Earnings
view.description: Average weekly earnings are derived by dividing total weekly earnings (including overtime earnings) by the number of employees. This data is compiled from the Survey of Employment, Payrolls and Hours which is a business census of non-farm payroll employees.

API & Download Information.Available Download Formats: CSV, JSON, PDF, RDF, RSS, XLS, XLSX, XML

Dataset Information.Attribution Source: Adapted from Statistics Canada, Cansim table 281-0026, This does not constitute an endorsement by Statistics Canada of this product.
